{"tid":774434,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[DSE中文勸世文]想中文考得好一定唔係靠背範文","createTime":"2018-08-10T10:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T05:58:21.000Z","uid":85866,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5b9b2198e67932d9533ffbeda3419d8c1a07a0b6","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"前言：唔少學校老師甚至補習社都鍾意叫學生背範文（話說如果好似林某人咁上堂讀完範文再叫學生番屋企背，咁點解要比錢補習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n事實上背範文係性價比極極極差既做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日會同大家講下正確讀範文既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先係範文佔卷一3成，姐係佔全卷7.2%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7.2％咩概念？一份大家睇唔起既SBA讀書報告大概係2％起跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（某d懶老師一份讀書報告計10％<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） <br />\n卷四佔14％，係範文既兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文底唔好既同學如果為左呢7.2%硬食十二篇（實際上十六篇）範文，等於浪費左大量操起其他卷既機會，神仙都難救<br />\n中文底好更加唔應該背。入大學最少計5科，比你中文由5操到上星星，其他科2233搵邊間收你？<br />\n<br />\n所以我無論自己溫定教人都唔會背範文（論仁論孝論君子可以背少少，少少就夠）<br />\n反而應該重點溫出最多既（1）中心思想；同（2）內容大意<br />\n大家溫書時亦應該問自己係唔係記得每一段大概講乜，記到已經可以溫下段<br />\n某d篇章（eg勸學）比較鍾意考寫作手法，但操熟咁多年寫作手法題的話（唔知係咩可以搵2014 Q3同2016 Q2做做，算係近年最入門既題目）已經識做，問題唔大<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔背範文唔代表唔溫<br />\n因為考評局重設範文都係想同學識多d文化概念（做唔做到就另一回事）<br />\n大家不妨將背左既範文用落作文／說話度，marker睇到肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（前提係唔好用錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家睇完可以比較有效率咁溫中文，有咩關於中文既問題可以隨便問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：教左幾年細補習社同日校，CE AL DSE都拎最高grade，而且唔係好似某人咁單考中文，每次都全科溫＋考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5c2f4666e0978062be8bd28ee38e66e3e2505f","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"做私補？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a12ce4afb861affbc3f2ffcec898f0e59a3a8b","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"5d5c2f4666e0978062be8bd28ee38e66e3e2505f","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"做私補？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"教緊大班，暫時唔接單個私補<br />\n<br />\n巴打有問題可以係度問／email我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我email：lauondaihkg@gmail.com"},{"pid":"729a98536761316cc05f9835b32e36921ce8cba7","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3a12ce4afb861affbc3f2ffcec898f0e59a3a8b","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"5d5c2f4666e0978062be8bd28ee38e66e3e2505f","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"做私補？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"教緊大班，暫時唔接單個私補<br />\n<br />\n巴打有問題可以係度問／email我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我email：lauondaihkg@gmail.com"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74d9c56526b588f4478053cd61fd233daeb51b3","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"729a98536761316cc05f9835b32e36921ce8cba7","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3a12ce4afb861affbc3f2ffcec898f0e59a3a8b","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"5d5c2f4666e0978062be8bd28ee38e66e3e2505f","tid":774434,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"做私補？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"教緊大班，暫時唔接單個私補<br />\n<br />\n巴打有問題可以係度問／email我架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我email：lauondaihkg@gmail.com"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T10:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:03:08.000Z","msg":"email會方便d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39500171a35a50d317d9b46ffa02a47245a3258","tid":774434,"uid":180156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"補中文已經係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd1571783f1b5f9b3c7c44e6e4a422e9b5113c2","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f39500171a35a50d317d9b46ffa02a47245a3258","tid":774434,"uid":180156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"補中文已經係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:37:50.000Z","msg":"如果肯自己仔細操晒咁多年卷再搵晒咁多年考評報告黎睇，點都會有d心得<br />\n問題係唔係個個有咁既時間，要考六科既話無可能科科都咁溫<br />\n加上有d概念唔係咁容易google，中六學生要搞清楚咩叫「仁」可能已經用左成個下午<br />\n所以補中文係幫手慳時間，當然本身天資過人／好多時間既自己溫都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3168a486d0b2db06432d07a9c3a6dc14627b8b44","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"都同意你嘅講法<br />\n範文唔係靠死背 而係要你了解佢背後想帶出咩意思<br />\n18dse可以見到，幾乎全部題目都係叫你用<span style=\"color: red;\">自己文字</span>作答，拎到分嘅關鍵唔係在於你可唔可以背到一篇文，而係你明唔明一篇文<br />\n咁當然，都要適量地背下啲語譯 佔唔少分之餘仲幫到你做後面嘅文言文<br />\n利申:18dse 中文閱讀5** 但作文3左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c552758c0e44ea2cc76fa215042abb68af82b48a","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3168a486d0b2db06432d07a9c3a6dc14627b8b44","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"都同意你嘅講法<br />\n範文唔係靠死背 而係要你了解佢背後想帶出咩意思<br />\n18dse可以見到，幾乎全部題目都係叫你用<span style=\"color: red;\">自己文字</span>作答，拎到分嘅關鍵唔係在於你可唔可以背到一篇文，而係你明唔明一篇文<br />\n咁當然，都要適量地背下啲語譯 佔唔少分之餘仲幫到你做後面嘅文言文<br />\n利申:18dse 中文閱讀5** 但作文3左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"其實語譯17年或之前佔10／8x，都叫值背<br />\n但而家都係佔5／100姐，唔太值得背，不如真係學巴打講理解下篇文<br />\n不過遲兩年佢會唔會改就無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74a937c2a7d94cc3d71b4e829174fa011adf71e","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c552758c0e44ea2cc76fa215042abb68af82b48a","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3168a486d0b2db06432d07a9c3a6dc14627b8b44","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"都同意你嘅講法<br />\n範文唔係靠死背 而係要你了解佢背後想帶出咩意思<br />\n18dse可以見到，幾乎全部題目都係叫你用<span style=\"color: red;\">自己文字</span>作答，拎到分嘅關鍵唔係在於你可唔可以背到一篇文，而係你明唔明一篇文<br />\n咁當然，都要適量地背下啲語譯 佔唔少分之餘仲幫到你做後面嘅文言文<br />\n利申:18dse 中文閱讀5** 但作文3左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"其實語譯17年或之前佔10／8x，都叫值背<br />\n但而家都係佔5／100姐，唔太值得背，不如真係學巴打講理解下篇文<br />\n不過遲兩年佢會唔會改就無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"因為我見level4至5** 啲grade係可以差幾分就一個grade，所以先咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，我見到份卷嘅時候都嚇左一跳 18dse啲範文根本益左無溫書嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78394432bba98c8f49d1bc424141a565fa82048","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a74a937c2a7d94cc3d71b4e829174fa011adf71e","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c552758c0e44ea2cc76fa215042abb68af82b48a","tid":774434,"uid":85866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3168a486d0b2db06432d07a9c3a6dc14627b8b44","tid":774434,"uid":199136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"都同意你嘅講法<br />\n範文唔係靠死背 而係要你了解佢背後想帶出咩意思<br />\n18dse可以見到，幾乎全部題目都係叫你用<span style=\"color: red;\">自己文字</span>作答，拎到分嘅關鍵唔係在於你可唔可以背到一篇文，而係你明唔明一篇文<br />\n咁當然，都要適量地背下啲語譯 佔唔少分之餘仲幫到你做後面嘅文言文<br />\n利申:18dse 中文閱讀5** 但作文3左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:03:03.000Z","msg":"其實語譯17年或之前佔10／8x，都叫值背<br />\n但而家都係佔5／100姐，唔太值得背，不如真係學巴打講理解下篇文<br />\n不過遲兩年佢會唔會改就無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"因為我見level4至5** 啲grade係可以差幾分就一個grade，所以先咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，我見到份卷嘅時候都嚇左一跳 18dse啲範文根本益左無溫書嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"睇sample paper都估到少少今年唔會好詳細咁考，但下年應該唔會咁放水喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88168cf248c83876ec81914503f40d3b7ff9a137","tid":774434,"uid":179757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"講真 範圍冇背過 12篇 最多淨係識背最短果六篇 同問答<br />\n今年考5🌟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n閱讀好講feel。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{